name: "The Salesman"
description:
This grave gave me such "The Death of a Salesman" vibes. The vast majority of graves in this mausoleum have plastic flowers in them; this one had none in their flower urn.
   I wanna bring you to where I keep my captured Souls; however, only 6 people may access it from this image before the portal closes, then this returns to being a simple art piece.
